-- Croatia May Delay Property Tax to 2014, Vecernji Reports
-- B y   J a s m i n a   K u z m a n o v i c
-- 2012-10-31T07:07:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-31/croatia-may-delay-property-tax-to-2014-vecernji-reports.html
Croatia may delay the introduction
of the property tax to 2014,  Vecernji List  reported, citing
unidentified government officials.  Previously, the tax was to be valid as of early next year,
Finance Minister Slavko Linic said on Oct. 24.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jasmina Kuzmanovic in Zagreb at 
 jkuzmanovic@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  